f6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuNAtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuNAtv.png&h=a8f19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反都出埋唔好再搵藉口唔出<br />\n1月1號維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家瞭解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received"},{"pid":"7e4db43d44ff5bdda969b80495e3487cfb5d7919","tid":1805531,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"計德國時間仲有幾個鐘咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=ddca9ab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a>"},{"pid":"73649b032ac9d13e95d2de7b9b07a2377f9bc187","tid":1805531,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"#CelebrationAnywhereButHK<br />\n<br />\n推上國際 香港2020跨年活動遭極權軍政府打壓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1805578\" data-auto-link target=\"_b